    "spell": {
        "name": "The Queen's Rainbow",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You tell the story of the Queen of Bees and her retinue trying to pass through a rainbow on their way to visit the King of Spiders. You conjure forth a large, transparent rainbow. Creatures who enter or begin their turn in the rainbow\u2019s space must succeed at a Fortitude saving throw or become dazzled for 1 round (or blinded for 1 round on a critical failure).",
